OL,3,COver #385 million funding settlement
OL,4,Cagreed for West Midlands
OL,6,FThe West Midlands Combined Authority
OL,7,Fhas been allocated over #385 million
OL,8,Fin government funding, granting it
OL,9,Fgreater control over spending
OL,10,Fdecisions.
OL,12,FThe Government says the money replaces
OL,13,Fthe previous system of bidding for
OL,14,Findividual funding pots and is part of
OL,15,Fa broader devolution strategy.
OL,17,FThe #388,623,471 funding will be used
OL,18,Facross transport, education, adult
OL,19,Fskills, housing, employment support,
OL,20,Fand economic growth.
