OL,6,FLocal leaders argue that having
OL,7,Fcontrol over spending decisions will
OL,8,Fallow for more efficient use of
OL,9,Fresources and better targeting of
OL,10,Flocal priorities.
OL,12,FHowever, some critics question how far
OL,13,Fthe money will go, given the
OL,14,Fsignificant challenges around housing
OL,15,Fshortages, skills training, and
OL,16,Fsluggish economic growth.
