OL,3,COver #385 million funding settlement
OL,4,Cagreed for West Midlands
OL,6,FThis new settlement follows previous
OL,7,Ffunding agreements, including the
OL,8,F#1.05 billion City Region Sustainable
OL,9,FTransport Settlement and other
OL,10,Fallocations that required multiple
OL,11,Fcompetitive bids.
OL,13,FCritics have long argued that the old
OL,14,Fsystem created uncertainty and
OL,15,Finefficiencies, making long-term
OL,16,Fplanning difficult for local
OL,17,Fauthorities.
