OL,3,COver #385 million funding settlement
OL,4,Cagreed for West Midlands
OL,6,FAngela Rayner, Secretary of State for
OL,7,FHousing, Communities and Local
OL,8,FGovernment, said: "Our country and
OL,9,Flocal leaders have been held back for
OL,10,Ftoo long by outdated systems and
OL,11,Fbureaucratic box-ticking exercises,
OL,12,Fstifling growth and ambition.
OL,14,F"West Midlands will now hold the reins
OL,15,Fon its own priorities ` driving
OL,16,Fforward meaningful change for working
OL,17,Fpeople from building more affordable
OL,18,Fhomes to day-to-day running of buses.
