OL,3,COver #385 million funding settlement
OL,4,Cagreed for West Midlands
OL,6,F"This is our devolution revolution in
OL,7,Faction, and we are bringing forward
OL,8,Fthis more flexible funding for more
OL,9,Fmayors next year to continue our Plan
OL,10,Ffor Change to spread opportunities and
OL,11,Fgrowth to every region."
OL,13,FWest Midlands Mayor Richard Parker,
OL,14,Fwho was elected in 2023, has
OL,15,Fpositioned himself as a strong
OL,16,Fadvocate for devolution and local
OL,17,Fdecision-making. He succeeded
OL,18,FConservative Andy Street in a closely
OL,19,Fcontested election and has prioritised
OL,20,Feconomic growth, housing, and skills
OL,21,Fdevelopment since taking office.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@XO]
