OL,4,Cagreed for West Midlands
OL,6,FParker said: "This settlement shows
OL,7,Fthe Government's strong confidence and
OL,8,Fcommitment in transferring more powers
OL,9,Fand responsibilities from Whitehall to
OL,10,Fthe West Midlands.
OL,12,F"That means every penny can be
OL,13,Ftargeted where it will have the
OL,14,Fbiggest impact, on the things that
OL,15,Fmatter most to people like jobs,
OL,16,Faffordable housing and better
OL,17,Ftransport ` all key priorities for me.
