OL,3,COver #385 million funding settlement
OL,4,Cagreed for West Midlands
OL,6,F"This initial pot of money is just the
OL,7,Fstart of a succession of multi-year
OL,8,Fsettlements for the region. In return,
OL,9,FI will use that money to make bold,
OL,10,Flong-term decisions that create real
OL,11,Fopportunities for local people, making
OL,12,Fsure no community is left behind."
OL,14,FGreater Manchester will receive nearly
OL,15,F#630m, though it also carries more
OL,16,Fresponsibilities, including policing
OL,17,Fand healthcare. Future settlements are
OL,18,Fexpected for other mayoral authorities.
